Package gobblin.data.management.conversion.hive.watermarker

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HiveSourceWatermarker
    An interface to read previous high watermarks and write new high watermarks to state.
    HiveSourceWatermarkerFactory
    An interface for creating new HiveSourceWatermarkers
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MultiKeyValueLongWatermark
    A Watermark that holds multiple key value watermarks.
    PartitionLevelWatermarker
    A HiveSourceWatermarker that maintains watermarks for each Partition.
    PartitionLevelWatermarker.Factory
    Factory to create a PartitionLevelWatermarker
    TableLevelWatermarker
    A HiveSourceWatermarker that manages Watermark at a per Table basis.
    TableLevelWatermarker.Factory
    Factory to create a TableLevelWatermarker
